UNDERSTAND HOW THIS VIRUS IS DIFFERENT & WHY A THREAT  Feeling confused as to why Coronavirus is a bigger deal than Seasonal flu? Here it is in a nutshell. I hope this helps. Feel free to share this to others who don‚Äôt understand...  It has to do with RNA sequencing.... I.e. genetics.  Seasonal flu is an ‚Äúall human virus‚Äù. The DNA/RNA chains that make up the virus are recognized by the human immune system. This means that your body has some immunity to it before it comes around each year... you get immunity two ways...through exposure to a virus  or by getting a flu shot.  Novel viruses  come from animals.... the WHO tracks novel viruses in animals  (sometimes for years watching for mutations). Usually these viruses only transfer from animal to animal (pigs in the case of H1N1) (birds in the case of the Spanish flu). But once  one of these animal viruses mutates  and starts to transfer from animals to humans... then it‚Äôs a problem  Why? Because we have no natural or acquired immunity.. the RNA sequencing of the genes inside the virus isn‚Äôt human  and the human immune system doesn‚Äôt recognize it so  we can‚Äôt fight it off.  Now.... sometimes  the mutation only allows transfer from animal to human  for years it‚Äôs only transmission is from an infected animal to a human before it finally mutates so that it can now transfer human to human... once that happens..we have a new contagion phase. And depending on the fashion of this new mutation  thats what decides how contagious  or how deadly it‚Äôs gonna be..  H1N1 was deadly....but it did not mutate in a way that was as deadly as the Spanish flu. It‚Äôs RNA was slower to mutate and it attacked its host differently  too.  Fast forward.  Now  here comes this Coronavirus... it existed in animals only  for nobody knows how long...but one day  at an animal market  in Wuhan China  in December 2019  it mutated and made the jump from animal to people. At first  only animals could give it to a person... But here is the scary part.... in just TWO WEEKS it mutated again and gained the ability to jump from human to human. Scientists call this quick ability  ‚Äúslippery‚Äù  This Coronavirus  not being in any form a ‚Äúhuman‚Äù virus (whereas we would all have some natural or acquired immunity). Took off like a rocket. And this was because  Humans have no known immunity...doctors have no known medicines for it.  And it just so happens that this particular mutated animal virus  changed itself in such a way the way that it causes great damage to human lungs..  That‚Äôs why Coronavirus is different from seasonal flu  or H1N1 or any other type of influenza.... this one is slippery AF. And it‚Äôs a lung eater...And  it‚Äôs already mutated AGAIN  so that we now have two strains to deal with  strain s  and strain L....which makes it twice as hard to develop a vaccine.  We really have no tools in our shed  with this. History has shown that fast and immediate closings of public places has helped in the past pandemics. Philadelphia and Baltimore were reluctant to close events in 1918 and they were the hardest hit in the US during the Spanish Flu.  Factoid: Henry VIII stayed in his room and allowed no one near him  till the Black Plague passed...(honestly...I understand him so much better now). Just like us  he had no tools in his shed  except social isolation...  And let me end by saying....right now it‚Äôs hitting older folks harder... but this genome is so slippery...if it mutates again (and it will). Who is to say  what it will do next. In a nut shell - a hospital services 460 000 people and they have 16 ICU beds with ventilators. If they are down to the last ventilator and there is a 70 old year and a 30 year old who both need one  the 30 year old will get it. This is why we are being asked to stay away from large gatherings - maybe not for you  because you may be young and healthy and may have limited symptoms but for those around you who might not. For your 70 year old neighbour who may not have access to that last ventilator because all 16 are being used.

MUST READ BY Charlie Anderson  GOD USES MAN'S HATRED  While the trial of President Trump is not over  I must call your attention to something momentous. We conservatives have seen what lengths Democrats will go in order to regain power.  We have recognized how power has corrupted them.  Although we know how Democrats intend to use political power  we have felt inadequate to stop them.  Of late many of us have wondered if it was possible to stop the Democrats without violence.   In many ways  our government no longer functions.   No significant legislation can be enacted as long as Democrats control either house of Congress.  Almost every Presidential executive order has been challenged by a liberal Federal judge.  Republican leadership has often been disappointing.  The conservative majority during the first two years was largely squandered by timid Republican leaders.  Just when things looked impossible for conservatives something miraculous happened. God used the hatred of Democrats for only ONE man to change the course of American history.  Donald Trump threatened the systemic corruption of the Democratic Party and the Deep State.  Unlike most politicians  he could not be bought off.  He was a counterpuncher and street brawler who refused to back down. Donald Trump would ruin Democratic Party plans for open borders  globalism  and business as usual in the Deep State. To top off their outrage  Trump needled and goaded the Democrats with his tweets and called them out publicly for their anti-American agenda.  I believe that Trump Derangement Syndrome was part of God‚Äôs plan.   At just the right moment for our country  Democratic Party leaders became so enraged at Donald Trump that they committed political suicide.  In the last three years Democrats have done nothing but attack President Trump and demonstrate their hatred of America.  Oblivious to common sense  Democratic leaders went out of their way to be stupid.   How stupid was it to torpedo the Democratic frontrunner in the presidential race by calling attention to Ukraine  where the frontrunner and other Democrats had corrupt dealings?   How stupid was it to alienate anyone who loved his country and supported our military?  How stupid was it to spend so much time enticing illegals across the border  protecting criminal aliens  and giving citizen benefits to illegals while ignoring human trafficking at the border  narcotic trafficking at the border  Mexican gangs flooding across the border  and the burden of illegals on taxpayers?  How stupid was it to repeatedly show no concern for newborn infants  young girls  female athletes  and victims of fake women?  How stupid was it to anger an entire region of our country by attempting to erase its history and its leaders?  How stupid was it to keep alienating half the voters by calling them insulting names  especially after  this strategy did so much for Hillary?  How stupid was it to defend our nation's enemies  invite them to bring their violent supremacist culture into America  and pander to their demands while ignoring the needs of Americans?  How stupid was it to continue fake victim causes like BLM after they were rejected by the majority  disproved by FBI statistics  and resulted in the murder of policemen?  How stupid was it to allow the most radical air-headed anti-American leftists on this planet to define the Democratic Party publicly?   How stupid was it to proceed with a partisan impeachment destined to fail?  How stupid was it to hold an impeachment extravaganza that featured paid witnesses who hurt the Democratic Party's false narrative?  How stupid was it to publicly announce the plan to impeach Trump immediately after his election?  How stupid was it to repeatedly change the reasons for impeachment?  How stupid was it to insist that Trump's impeachment articles required haste because he was so dangerous  but these charges were not urgent enough to send to the Senate for over a month?  How stupid was it to have the House impeachment show run by professional liars who hid evidence  hid witnesses  manufactured evidence  yet pretended to be prayerful and solemn?  How stupid was the Speaker of the House when she passed out golden pens at her signing of the impeachment articles  as if she was the author of the Magna Carta?  How stupid was it to demand that the Senate perform the investigative obligations of the House?  How stupid was it to delay the Articles long enough to prevent Democratic candidates from campaigning in Iowa?  How stupid was it for the new Virginia governor to go for a massive gun grab in an election year?   By Divine intervention  Democratic leaders have administered a Samurai sword to their own bellies since Trump was elected. With three years to come up with a likable moderate candidate with a positive message  the Democratic Party has produced a political freak show of unelectable radicals. Such is the power of hatred to cloud human judgement.  All the media hype and money that will be poured into the 2020 presidential race by Democrats cannot obscure the bankruptcy of Democratic leadership. Their candidates reek with hypocrisy  corruption  pandering  fascism  and socialism.  The wheels have come off the Democratic band wagon. Having dug a huge grave for themselves  they are so enraged by hatred of Donald Trump that they have accelerated their digging.  They want more witnesses  a longer trial  more distraction from their own candidates  with no possibility of winning.    Unlike the "suicide" of Jeffrey Epstein  the suicide of the Democratic Party was not predictable. Although I appreciate the hard work of our President  I see a larger hand here than that of Donald Trump or Republican leaders. It is now possible to believe that Democrats have inflicted such grievous wounds on themselves that they will lose everything in November--the House  the Senate  and the Presidency.  God has provided us with suicidal Democratic behavior.  If the British can stomp their liberal Democrats  we can stomp ours in November. In the meanwhile  I don‚Äôt mind seeing the dirt continue to fly out of their hole.  "Praise be to God  who delivers more than we can ask or think."
